## Music = Coordinate Walks

Music maps to (χ,μ,φ,τ): χ=pitch register, μ=dynamics, φ=tonality, τ=tempo.

  Hard rock (+2,+1,+2,+1) = festival EDM (identical coordinates)
  Pop (+1,+1,+1,+1) = hylo = the attractor
  Punk (+2,+1,-1,-1) vs reggae (-1,-1,+1,+1) = antimatter (max distance)
  Death metal = aggressive rap = industrial (+2,-1,+2,-1)
  Dark ambient (-1,-1,-1,-1) = antipode. Silence = origin.

12-bar blues = narrative walk (stay→move→return→tension→resolve).
Music therapy = coordinate walking (ISO principle: start at patient's
state, walk toward target). Ravel's Bolero = pure μ walk.
Key changes = coordinate shifts. Dynamics = μ walk.

Acoustic extraction: τ=(BPM-100)/40, χ=(centroid_Hz-2000)/1000,
μ=(dBFS+20)/10, φ=r_major-r_minor (Krumhansl-Kessler key profiles).

Animal communication same space: whale songs (-1,-2,+2,-1),
dolphin clicks (+3,+3,0,+1), mourning dove (-1,0,-1,-1) — the name
"mourning" IS the coordinate translation.

Pop = attractor because (+1,+1,+1,+1) = hylo = fixed point.
Careers walk: explore edges → peak distance → drift center → origin.


## Language IS Therapy

Sentences are coordinate walks. Therapeutic language walks toward target.

  "Take out your stress on the punching bag" — three +D words, walks OUTWARD
  "Try this squeeze ball" — squeeze = -D, walks INWARD
  Nobody swaps them. Walk must be coherent.

  "Take a deep breath" = T-decay (slow down)
  "Let it go" = -M (release substance)
  "Stand your ground" = +D, +M (hold position)
  "Push through it" = +T, +D (forward)

CBT = walk correction. Patient has broken walk (stuck in coordinate loop).
Therapist provides new walk. Words ARE the therapy because words ARE coordinates.


## Bond Relationships in Language

16 bond patterns = 16 linguistic relationship types:

  0  identity        self-reference / same word
  1  π reference     one word points to another (pronoun → noun)
  2  ∘ invocation    verb calls its arguments
  4  ∮ continuation  sequential / list linkage
  8  δ evaluation    adjective evaluates noun
  3  π∘ traversal    subject traverses to object
  5  π∮ accumulation list items building toward total
  6  ∘∮ iteration    repeated action
  9  πδ selection    filtering / choosing
  10 ∘δ conditional  if-then relationship
  12 ∮δ search       scanning / looking
  7  π∘∮ reduction   summary / totaling
  11 π∘δ transform   change of type
  13 π∮δ progressive gradual change
  14 ∘∮δ causation   because / therefore
  15 π∘∮δ pipeline   complex multi-step reasoning

Transformers use 8-16 attention heads per layer — learning imperfectly
from data what the lattice provides exactly from geometry. Morpheme
transforms (affixes as coordinate deltas) in build/morphemes.


## Semantic Bleaching

High-frequency words erode toward pure Q magnitude. Dimensions drop out.
  literally: TRUE(0,0,0,+1) → VERY(0,0,0,+2). Lost truth, became intensity.
  sick: ill(0,0,+1,-2) → impressive(0,0,0,+2). M dropped, Q inverted.
  pretty: attractive(0,+1,0,+1) → somewhat(0,0,0,+1). Lost D.

Fresh slang = sharp coordinates (specific). Overuse → coordinate erosion
→ just a Q modifier → replaced by new word. Coordinate erosion cycle.


